/* ft calendar customiztion */
.fc-cal-day-umber {
  background-color: #fff1e5;
  color: #33302e;
  font-family: "Titillium Web Regular";
  border: none;
}

.fc-cal-date-normal-umber {
  background-color: #fff1e5;
  color: #33302e;
  font-family: "Titillium Web Regular";
  border: none;
}

.fc-cal-date-normal-umber:hover {
  background-color: #000000;
  color: #ffffff;
  font-family: "Titillium Web Regular";
  border: none;
}

.fc-cal-date-disabled-umber {
  background-color: #fff1e5;
  color: rgba(51, 48, 46, 0.5);
  font-family: "Titillium Web Regular";
  border: none;
}

.fc-cal-month-header-umber {
  background-color: #000000;
  font-family: "Titillium Web Regular";
}

.fc-cal-weekend-umber {
  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
}

.fc-cal-container-umber {
  border: none;
}

.fc-cal-nav-next-umber,
.fc-cal-nav-prev-umber {
  font-family: "Titillium Web Regular";
  font-size: 12px;
}

.fc-cal-date-selected-umber {
  background-color: #000000;
  color: #ffffff;
  font-family: "Titillium Web Regular";
}

.fc-cal-date-selected-umber:hover {
  background-color: #000000;
  color: #ffffff;
  font-family: "Titillium Web Regular";
}
